{
  "texts": [
    "IntroductionThe volume of biomedical documents has increased considerably since medical records were digitized.",
    "The patient-doctor interactions also lead to a considerable increase in biomedical papers.",
    "With more than 3500 documents added daily to different journals.",
    "Pubmed has around 36 million citations and abstracts of biomedical literature [1].",
    "All these resources provide a valuable source of information to health practitioners, doctors, and researchers."
  ]
}